sequenceDiagram
    title Order Processing Flow

    actor Customer
    participant WebApp
    participant API
    participant Database

    Customer->>WebApp: Place Order
    WebApp->>API: POST /orders
    API->>Database: INSERT order

    alt Order valid
        Database-->>API: Success
        API-->>WebApp: 201 Created
        WebApp-->>Customer: Order Confirmed
    else Order invalid
        Database-->>API: Error
        API-->>WebApp: 400 Bad Request
        WebApp-->>Customer: Please fix errors
    end

    loop Every 5 seconds
        WebApp->>API: GET /order/status
        API-->>WebApp: Status update
    end

    Note over WebApp,API: Async processing
